Gas Routing Flowchart — GEMS

This flowchart outlines the internal gas movement pathway during emergency oxygen production.
It illustrates how oxygen-bearing gas moves from the Processing Core through the system’s stabilization structures and out to the habitat interface.

This chart is intended for:

engineers reviewing flow logic,

validation of component order,

integration with thermal and failure-mode analysis.

It represents functional sequence, not mechanical complexity.

ACS-2 Gas Routing Flowchart
                   ┌──────────────────────────┐
                   │  START: Emergency Trigger │
                   │  (Low O₂ / System Fault)  │
                   └───────────────┬──────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                   ┌──────────────────────────┐
                   │   Processing Core Warmup │
                   │ (Heat-up → gas generation)│
                   └───────────────┬──────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                   ┌──────────────────────────┐
                   │     Isolation Gate       │
                   │   (One-way gas routing)  │
                   └───────────────┬──────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
        ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
        │       Buffer / Stabilization Manifold             │
        │  - Smooths pulses                                 │
        │  - Regulates pressure                             │
        └───────────────┬──────────────────────────────────┘
                        │
                        ▼
          ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
          │            Output Regulator                  │
          │  (Flow control → Pressure shaping)           │
          └───────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘
                          │
                          ▼
        ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
        │       Habitat Interface / Emergency Feed          │
        │  - Atmosphere loop                                │
        │  - EVA shelters                                   │
        │  - Pressure stabilization                         │
        └───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

